      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest character and signs of regular use, but it's still got plenty of life left for the right owner! It\u2019s a practical choice for someone looking for reliable transportation at a great value.",
