    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been cared for with the highest level of attention. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history available. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
